column1: I was just wondering if anyone has traveled and gone through customs, etc after returning to CA from Asia and what to expect with customs/health check. Any assistance would be appreciated. I’m a US citizen traveling to Singapore and Malaysia then having a night in Japan before heading back to the US.
Here is the CDC guidance: https:/…after-travel-precautions.htmlMalaysia, Singapore, and Japan are not Level 3 countries.
